                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 11 月 7 日消息，黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标现已在京东开售，该款鼠标搭载原相 PAW3395 传感器、支持三模连接，<strong>售价 139 元</strong>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1351" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/2e1fb576-e9fb-479f-8ea1-91092bb1201a.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExOC5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_12,x_12,a_0/format,f_auto" title="黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标开售：原相 PAW3395、三模连接，139 元" width="769" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/wGjLn1Q" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img14.360buyimg.com/pop/jfs/t1/135784/10/49418/8893/6718afc1F8de8bfd3/b43e4f37c0341232.jpg" title="黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标开售：原相 PAW3395、三模连接，139 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标</span></span><span class="card-abstract">原相 PAW3395 | 三模连接</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 139 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1737" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/72c5fc5a-7c71-4769-92dd-b5e192c094d6.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExNi5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_12,x_12,a_0/format,f_auto" title="黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标开售：原相 PAW3395、三模连接，139 元" width="756" /></p><p>据介绍，黑爵 AJ159 NL P 鼠标采用星闪连接方案，配备 <strong>1K Nano 无线接收器</strong>（理论延迟约 1ms）。鼠标内置 <strong>800mAh 电池</strong>，支持星闪、有线、蓝牙<strong>三模连接</strong>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1226" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/85171c43-d49c-4193-866b-f5e8036bf8e9.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzEyMi5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_12,x_12,a_0/format,f_auto" title="黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标开售：原相 PAW3395、三模连接，139 元" width="796" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1060" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/a70fae1b-e61f-453e-8e5d-fcd02d805464.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzExOS5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_12,x_12,a_0/format,f_auto" title="黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标开售：原相 PAW3395、三模连接，139 元" width="776" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1038" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/1de82900-fa68-44e5-bf9a-dbb02ccc94e1.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzEyMi5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_12,x_12,a_0/format,f_auto" title="黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标开售：原相 PAW3395、三模连接，139 元" width="790" /></p><p>该款鼠标搭载<strong>原相 PAW3395 传感器</strong>，支持 100-26000DPI 可调、650IPS 追踪速率、50G 加速度。黑爵 AJ159 NL 全系左右按键采用华诺绿透白点微动开关（<strong>1 亿次点击寿命</strong>）、滚轮为丰实卫奇编码器（100 万圈）。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1276" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/2be56ece-40d1-48bb-9d95-a39cebd7d34d.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzEyMi5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_12,x_12,a_0/format,f_auto" title="黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标开售：原相 PAW3395、三模连接，139 元" width="792" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1186" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/6c1cdb68-63e6-4206-8ce8-9357635de380.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzEyMy5wbmc=,t_100,g_9,y_12,x_12,a_0/format,f_auto" title="黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标开售：原相 PAW3395、三模连接，139 元" width="799" /></p><p style="text-align: left;">IT之家附黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标产品参数如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1204" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/f761076c-8a8e-4598-a8c7-a7113f34e9ee.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xdy9xdzk2LnBuZw==,t_100,g_9,y_10,x_10,a_0/format,f_auto" title="黑爵 AJ159 NL P 星闪鼠标开售：原相 PAW3395、三模连接，139 元" width="622" /></p><p>2024 年 11.11 大促全网好价合集：<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fcontentlist%3Fapi%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnapi.ithome.com%252Fapi%252Ftopmenu%252Fgetmenufeeds%252F166%252F0